Refactor album and user repositories to use generic base repository pattern
- Updated AlbumService and AlbumRepository to return PageResult for pagination. - Refactored AlbumHandler and PublicHandler to accommodate new service response structure. - Simplified UserRepository and UserGroupRepository by embedding base repository for common CRUD operations. - Removed unused methods and cleaned up code for better readability and maintainability. - Adjusted email service and authentication logic for improved error handling and user experience. - Updated asset subproject commit to reflect changes.
